 Bally 还是致敬品牌传统和户外元素。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114147p7eYZCcFVt5IWa1X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114140wib7aHNXTlCQ9edh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114141bVhm2BIEwvYcTGZk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114140OesRy5gQzvYcTd8U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114146RnV8DpYbZQlBNHAm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114147fPxVbpj5XlAEBmLM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261141489QA05Oe3vFxDi2WK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114151yLNRXd3SktFU87lI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114153gfXuBZLhADFcxwCK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114154T9Vw4xeBfRFUjQWt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114157uhyVWSkdR8TsDQxz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114158kNtcdAMaBy8UueL1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114200fhYSak4z1ybtFGmL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114200uUPq9Qv8ZsoxVfr1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114200quN8tzGERXdBQJ5g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114203xD6MXasQ8A2lt3Op.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/kith-champion-collaboration-\" rel=\"nofollow\">KITH 与 Champion 合作</a>，女装系列将首次登陆 KITH 官网、门店，以及 NET-A-PORTER 全球同步发售。 </p><p>此外，KITH 主理人 Ronnie Fieg 在 Instagram 上发布了几张 Champion 合作款男装系列的图片，破天荒地把 Champion 标志性的 logo 改成了彩色的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113754SzjQk3C1wbAdKEBa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113827o0ZEujxnC1sdYmX5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113756idsjDUpl5JB3hrRY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261137587KbGVBwYr0HgQEW2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113758QO9urGnJS1yaDMlE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113758R1Ug9Tmi4wDzoWdt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113759HRYShtlgK3jQpzn4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261137592yshTx1f8o7K4tC5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113800WPqumsEJ4ZOxr1yi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261139286JiFe91oY8qPSugp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261139090RVsuQ9XBlHYATmk.png\" data-ratio=\"0.864217\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113909amLUiQ5vVtnSJ1eE.png\" data-ratio=\"0.875200\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>老佛爷<a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Karl-Lagerfeld-launches-beachwear-collection-produced-by-Area-B,951511.html#.WpOAOJP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Karl Lagerfeld </a>在忙着到处签合约。 </p><p>目前，他的个人同名品牌与 Marchon 眼镜产销合同签到了 2023 年，又和意大利制造商 Giada 合作，生产和分销 Karl Lagerfeld 牛仔系列。现在，他又宣布将与法国品牌 Vilebrequin 合作，将于今年夏天推出全新的沙滩装系列。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226114219J6mkUw9QuCoD2cAy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.503077\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>怪招频出的时装周舞台，<a href=\"2018/https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/jil-sander-fall-2018-mfw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jil Sander </a>一如既往地简洁。 </p><p>这一季里，设计师 Lucie 与 Luke Meier 用羊毛、透明硬纱、针织面料配合立体轮廓，带来了一个关于未来的系列。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113545L6BrY9lCPhziFoHf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261135458h5Va6XyDtQ1suCr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113545ouJQzN47U2KtPMjs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113546TVhtyGYgwkcfW84d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113546x3htEQsczaOIfZv8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018022611354697wfjE4AYIKhpo18.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113546qdryoRs12uihvxAS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261135474B6INwesvLGEQk9f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018022611354706eoukHfJ3IbQnjB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261135476PXe2wsMx0HZYaUb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113548vQfFb2TdVeCE6lPY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113548RBAZyuOgLrztPiHS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113548W9NU6C5vmJOzriu1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113549zaSPEJgGef02m8pT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113549gay2HLhfsIodY5Qu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113549SOMGUh9jYrXoCFmL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802261135496v0491S5EIMFeTtm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180226113550kwbfxAplUHJCPh4g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <im